        <span style="font-size: 1.3em;">­ƒÆí</span>
        <span>Suggestions d'am├®lioration</span>
        <span style="background: #92400E; color: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 12px; margin-left: auto;">${totalCount}</span>
